{"tid":1268672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好放棄任何希望","createTime":"2019-06-30T10:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T10:47:42.000Z","uid":149901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0f40ae5f5840d72f274639519ab6988720bf5d","tid":1268672,"uid":149901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"個政府一日仲喺度，我哋一定要堅守落去<br />\n呢個6月香港人經歷好多事，我哋可能太慢令大家感到絕望，但請任何人都唔好放棄一絲希望，只有香港人可以救香港，俾個機會大家一齊行埋落去，抗爭到底<br />\n唔好再作出犧牲<br />\n<br />\n見到再有人犧牲真係好心痛，如果大家發現自己情緒有啲唔對路，要相信身邊嘅人或者我哋，我哋會聆聽你，同你一齊撐落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190630&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59772467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190630%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59772467&d=ZcVshzlQZ77dxUPC5JM1BE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=626db207\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190630%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59772467&h=4fb6c29e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190630&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59772467</a>"}]}